Since no one replied to his offer, Daemos started to plan his next moves.

Daemos:
Computer, trace geographical profile for this region accounting for the 
presence of energon.

After observing his findings, he decided to land and to put his plan to 
work. As he disembarked the Hellgate, he felt glad that this was a good 
spot. He drew some seeds of an odd aspect from a tube he had been carrying 
and spread them on the ground. They immediatly started to grow and were soon 
sprouts.

Daemos:
Perfect! While this is going on, I better check the Hellgate's systems...
